lse = auto-derived from name (may 404 / hit wrong page — spot-check before trusting)\",\n      \"sector\": \"Primary sector partition key used by Codex sector workers and UI filtering\",\n      \"description\": \"Concise company description for search, semantic matching, and outreach context\"\n    },\n    \"recruiter_links_note\": \"recruiter_search_url is a name-based LinkedIn People search ('<company> recruiter') that works for every company without needing the exact company page slug — open it to see current recruiters, then paste individual profile URLs into recruiters[]. Each company has a unique 'id' (C0001...) so the list is countable/verifiable. NOTE: the first ~263 entries are curated with HQ/size/company-slug; the bulk entries carry verified real names + working recruiter links, with HQ/slug left blank to enrich.\",\n    \"total_companies\": 54,\n    \"notes\": \"Sector working file for EV / Energy. Codex agents edit only this file; the orchestrator merges sector files back into canonical recruiter.json.\",\n    \"ui_directory\": \"recruiter-directory/ (Next.js searchable UI with direct LinkedIn links + CSV export)\",\n    \"population_progress\": \"Codex sector split. 873 companies populated with 1937 total recruiters; 1250 company descriptions missing. Merge run: 2026-06-01\",\n    \"partition_type\": \"sector\",\n    \"sector\": {\n      \"key\": \"energy\",\n      \"label\": \"EV / Energy\"\n    },\n    \"source_file\": \"job/recruiter.json\",\n    \"last_partition_build\": \"2026-06-01T00:45:06.200Z\"\n  },\n  \"companies\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"C0168\",\n      \"name\": \"NextEra Energy / FPL\",\n      \"category\": \"Energy Tech\",\n      \"sector\": \"energy\",\n      \"description\": \"NextEra Energy owns Florida Power & Light and develops regulated utility, renewable generation, battery storage, and grid infrastructure across North America.\",\n      \"hq_location\": \"Juno Beach, FL\",\n      \"priority\": 3,\n      \"size_estimate\": \"15k+\",\n      \"has_intern_program\": true,\n      \"linkedin_company_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/company/nextera-energy/\",\n      \"linkedin_url_verified\": true,\n      \"recruiter_search_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=NextEra%20Energy%20/%20FPL%20recruiter\",\n      \"careers_url\": \"\",\n      \"recruiters\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"Taylor Haines\",\n          \"title\": \"Associate Early Talent Recruiter\",\n          \"linkedin_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/taylorhaines561\",\n          \"email\": \"\",\n          \"location\": \"West Palm Beach, FL area\",\n          \"focus_area\": \"Early Talent / Campus Recruiting / Summer Internship Programs\",\n          \"connected\": false,\n          \"messaged\": false,\n          \"responded\": false,\n          \"date_contacted\": \"\",\n          \"notes\": \"Directly involved in campus recruiting and summer internship programs nationwide at NextEra Energy.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"Christine Mercier\",\n          \"title\": \"Recruiting Manager, College Relations\",\n          \"linkedin_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/christine-mercier-53525020\",\n          \"email\": \"\",\n          \"location\": \"United States\",\n          \"focus_area\": \"College Relations / University Recruiting Leadership\",\n          \"connected\": false,\n          \"messaged\": false,\n          \"responded\": false,\n          \"date_contacted\": \"\",\n          \"notes\": \"Leads the College Relations / university recruiting team overseeing intern and new grad efforts.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"Brad Ditrick\",\n          \"title\": \"Program Manager, IT Early Career Programs\",\n          \"linkedin_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/brad-ditrick-56152261\",\n          \"email\": \"\",\n          \"location\": \"United States\",\n          \"focus_area\": \"IT / Tech Early Career Programs (strong for SWE/AI interns)\",